---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Docs | Bilingual Stack" description="Starter documentation for the bilingual Astro template.">
  <article class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none">
    <h1>Documentation</h1>
    <p>
      This starter keeps the first release intentionally small: bilingual routes,
      typed content, basic quality checks, and optional smoke tests.
    </p>
    <h2>Recommended Checks</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>pnpm run check:content</code></li>
      <li><code>pnpm run check:links</code></li>
      <li><code>pnpm test</code></li>
      <li><code>pnpm run build</code></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
